metadata.name: You pick the name
metadata.description: Welcome to Berkley Rose Studio. Each NFT is an original gritty graffiti art piece that we have uniquely created. Each piece represents an important attribute and virtue in life. This collection may represent different things to different people. We want you to pick the name of your artwork. We hope that our art work will create some inspiring ideas, significant insights or simply bring a smile to your face. Enjoy collecting our unusual paintings that speak to your heart.
